releases.body: * fix ability to set custom file pattern per configuration repository

* #47 adds support for referencing templates and specifying parameters
 * #32 adds better support for YAML aliases 
 * #46 introduces format_version field, with future work for v2 format 
 * #35 default file pattern is now `.gocd.yaml` or `.gocd.yml`

* added configrepo material type
 * added p4 material type support
